Value.value: A rich smell of incense and a crackling fire cannot quite disguise the strong, earthy funk of animal hair. A large bucket of saddle soap is the source of an eye-watering vapour. Your host extends a genial hand.
Above the clamour of a busy workshop and the spit and hiss of burning logs, you cannot hear anything else.
Your host appears to be a man of middle years, with the rotund figure of a comfortable merchant. Appearances can be deceiving, however
